column2: SELECT s.subclass, specobjid, s.objID, s.dered_u, s.dered_g, s.dered_i, s.dered_z, s.dec, p.pmDec, p.pmRa, t.j, t.h, t.k into mydb.MyTable from SpecPhoto as s JOIN ProperMotions as p ON p.objID = s.objID JOIN TwoMass as t on t.objID = s.objID WHERE (s.subclass LIKE #) AND (s.subclass NOT LIKE #) ORDER BY s.subclass ASC
